Structure of a Theme
--------------------

| 
| 
| 
| 
**A Theme is a Module**  
|(without Python Logic)

Structure of a Theme
--------------------

* My Theme
	* static
  		* src
			* js, css, font, xml, img
	* data
		* my_theme.xml 
		* snippets.xml
		* options.xml
		* [ ... ]
	* views
		* pages.xml (static pages)



